{"tid":2212273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做3分鐘問卷 換 免費塔羅占卜！","createTime":"2020-09-21T16:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T21:24:38.000Z","uid":112513,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"adec4d9ea086e5d1585268afcba85426d4211c05","tid":2212273,"uid":112513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:08:21.000Z","msg":"打擾曬<br />\n件事係咁既，冇你幫手，可能畢唔到業。<br />\n事關我做緊fyp要收data，但因為轉過題目，而家要係半個月內收250份，時間十分緊湊(;&acute;༎ຶД༎ຶ`)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">只要你係男仔，都可以幫到手<br />\n全部MC ，3分鐘做完</span></strong><br />\n做完問卷你都會有得著，真既 (｡&igrave; _ &iacute;｡)<br />\n<br />\n搭車，痾屎，發吽哣既時候，㩒條link就可以做<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/5PCsxrk8dhKQ4HAA6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F5PCsxrk8dhKQ4HAA6&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=3bbbae78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/5PCsxrk8dhKQ4HAA6</a><br />\n<br />\n為表誠意，如果大家有興趣既話可以免費幫大家做塔羅占卜，可以係下面留言，收齊問卷就會順住答 <em>(如果想聽詳細啲可以留telegram)</em><br />\n<br />\n真係唔該曬，好人一生平安。"},{"pid":"81524cfc9b60b54b2742a36f8f13c1d6de767335","tid":2212273,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開過個j圖求做問卷post可能仲熱鬧"},{"pid":"7e46a0bfa7da39118e52d3b705c3434f1a0462d8","tid":2212273,"uid":112513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81524cfc9b60b54b2742a36f8f13c1d6de767335","tid":2212273,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" cla